-gon-khong-gian.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>H\u1ea1 th\u1ea5p tr\u1ea7n&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u1ed1ng, nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ea1 th\u1ea5p tr\u1ea7n s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng mang t\u1edbi c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n. Vi\u1ec7c s\u01a1n tr\u1ea7n b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0u t\u1ed1i h\u01a1n t\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed9 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ea7n nh\u00e0 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf.&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"724\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/ha-thap-tran-1024x724.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10824\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/ha-thap-tran-1024x724.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/ha-thap-tran-300x212.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/ha-thap-tran-768x543.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/ha-thap-tran.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>K\u00e9o cao kh\u00f4ng gian&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n nay nh\u1eefng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 tr\u1ea7n kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5p, g\u00e2y n\u00ean c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, ng\u1ed9t ng\u1ea1t. L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u01a1n t\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u t\u1ed1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea7n nh\u00e0 m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tr\u1ea7n cao h\u01a1n.&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"724\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/keo-cao-khong-gian-1024x724.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10825\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/keo-cao-khong-gian-1024x724.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/keo-cao-khong-gian-300x212.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/keo-cao-khong-gian-768x543.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/keo-cao-khong-gian.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>N\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng gian<\/strong><strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>S\u01a1n t\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda sau v\u00e0 tr\u1ea7n nh\u00e0 c\u00f9ng m\u00e0u v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i h\u01a1n c\u00e1c m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00ean s\u1ebd l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p th\u00f4ng minh gi\u00fap kh\u01a1i n\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea1t h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng h\u1eb9p ho\u1eb7c khu v\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh lang.&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"724\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/noi-rong-khong-gian-1024x724.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10826\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/noi-rong-khong-gian-1024x724.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/noi-rong-khong-gian-300x212.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/noi-rong-khong-gian-768x543.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/noi-rong-khong-gian.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Thu h\u1eb9p kh\u00f4ng gian<\/strong><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian qu\u00e1 r\u1ed9ng, l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u01a1n t\u01b0\u1eddng hai b\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n m\u00e0u t\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i n\u1ec1 v\u00e0 tr\u1ea7n s\u01a1n m\u00e0u s\u00e1ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian b\u1ecb thu h\u1eb9p l\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ecb gi\u00e1c. Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i.&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"724\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/thu-hep-khong-gian-1024x724.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10827\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/thu-hep-khong-gian-1024x724.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/thu-hep-khong-gian-300x212.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/thu-hep-khong-gian-768x543.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/thu-hep-khong-gian.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>R\u00fat ng\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng gian<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n kh\u00e1 r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u1ea5m c\u00fang, g\u1ea7n g\u0169i h\u01a1n h\u00e3y d\u00f9ng m\u00e0u s\u01a1n t\u1ed1i cho b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda sau v\u00e0 d\u00f9ng m\u00e0u s\u00e1ng ph\u1ee7 tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u00e1c n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c.&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"724\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/rut-ngan-khong-gian-1024x724.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10828\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/rut-ngan-khong-gian-1024x724.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/rut-ngan-khong-gian-300x212.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/rut-ngan-khong-gian-768x543.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/rut-ngan-khong-gian.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Nh\u1ea5n m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e3y gi\u1eef n\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0u s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n, trong khi s\u01a1n nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c b\u1eb1ng gam m\u00e0u t\u1ed1i. Hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u1eeb ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap thu h\u00fat \u00e1nh nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"724\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/nhan-mot-buc-tuong-1024x724.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10829\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/nhan-mot-buc-tuong-1024x724.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/nhan-mot-buc-tuong-300x212.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/nhan-mot-buc-tuong-768x543.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/nhan-mot-buc-tuong.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>C\u1eaft ng\u0103n t\u01b0\u1eddng&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng trong ph\u00f2ng m\u00ecnh tr\u00f4ng ng\u1eafn h\u01a1n, h\u00e3y s\u01a1n m\u00e0u t\u1ed1i v\u00e0o ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u00ecn ng\u1eafn h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"724\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/cat-ngan-tuong-1024x724.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10830\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/cat-ngan-tuong-1024x724.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/cat-ngan-tuong-300x212.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/cat-ngan-tuong-768x543.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/cat-ngan-tuong.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y <a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Byzan<\/a> \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb 9 c\u00e1ch thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u s\u1eafc.&nbsp;V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c m\u00e0u s\u1eafc kh\u00e1c nhau s\u1ebd cho ta c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng gian kh\u00e1c nhau, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1eb9o \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 h\u00f4 bi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. <\/p>\r\n